text.Prompt:
Your client has asked you to write a product description using item keywords and item specification below. You are an amazing copy writer so please write a fun product description.

Item specification:
CY Graphic Design Limited Quantity Cover Case For ZTE Source N9511 / Majesty Z796C (Include a CYstore Stylus Pen) - Seamless Antique Swirls

Item keywords:
This two pieces snap-on image with rubber coated case makes your cell phone has truly unique style
Special design provides protection from scratches
Unique design allows easy access to all buttons, controls and ports without having to remove the case
Material: Hard plastic image with thin rubber coating
With a very nice CYstore Stylus Pen
Easy to install: Just snap on.

Product description:
text.Response A:
Behold the CY Graphic Design Limited Quantity Cover Case for ZTE Source N9511 / Majesty Z796C, a veritable masterpiece of cellular protection and stylish flair! This deftly crafted case boasts not one, but two exquisite snap-on pieces, each adorned with an elegant antique swirl design that imbues your mobile device with an air of sophistication and refinement.

The sturdy hard plastic construction and thin rubber coating of this marvelous case provide unparalleled protection against the rigors of daily use, safeguarding your cherished device from the perils of scratches and scuffs. The seamless design allows for unfettered access to all buttons, controls, and ports, ensuring that your mobile experience remains unencumbered and uninterrupted.

This remarkable case also comes equipped with a CYstore Stylus Pen, a versatile and convenient accessory that enhances the functionality of your device. With this thoughtful addition, you can effortlessly navigate your phone's touchscreen with precision and accuracy, while the pen's sleek and ergonomic design ensures a comfortable grip and effortless use.

The installation process is a breeze, as the case simply snaps onto your device with ease, affording you the freedom to enjoy your phone's full potential without any hassle or fuss. Whether you're a tech-savvy connoisseur or a stylish trendsetter, this Limited Quantity Cover Case for ZTE Source N9511 / Majesty Z796C is the perfect choice for anyone seeking a balance of protection, style, and functionality.

So why wait? Elevate your mobile experience with this extraordinary case today and experience the unparalleled quality and craftsmanship that CY Graphic Design has to offer.
text.Response B: Looking for a phone case that's both stylish and functional? Look no further than the CY Graphic Design Limited Quantity Cover Case for the ZTE Source N9511 / Majesty Z796C. This two-piece snap-on case features a hard plastic image with a thin rubber coating, providing protection from scratches and a unique style all in one. The special design allows easy access to all buttons, controls, and ports without having to remove the case, and the included CYstore Stylus Pen adds even more functionality. Plus, with a limited quantity available, this case is sure to make a statement. So why wait? Order yours today and take your cell phone style to the next level!
